{"tid":208043,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"教同事妻練習靜脈注射　消防員遭控強吻","createTime":"2017-04-19T09:28:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T10:49:21.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6c456f0a53a535f1ab07a219f4140eabd1fcc245","tid":208043,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T09:28:45.000Z","msg":"桃園一名22歲劉姓消防隊員，遭同事的老婆（25歲）控告，涉嫌在去年11月9日晚間在劉員租屋處教她練習靜脈注射時，將她強壓在衣櫃以手環抱她的腰，強吻她；其後利用載她回家時，在小客車上以手按壓她的肩膀，再度強吻她。<br />\n<br />\n劉員供稱係對方欲報考消防員，且他的同事也曾在眾人面前明示，如果他的老婆有需要指導的，請他們指導，當天也是因為她想要練習，才會找他，堅決否認強吻對方。<br />\n<br />\n由於雙方事後仍正常且頻繁以LINE簡訊連繫，檢察官認為一般人若遭他人強吻，應感到害怕及羞愧而不願與對方有所接觸；且女子也反常地未在第一時間將個人發生的事告知丈夫，事後一個多月後才到派出所提告，今以罪證不足將劉員不起訴處分。（突發中心張沛森／桃園報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-n-xrj5dTEtc/U8LnkwPfQJI/AAAAAAAAI6k/hJnAtti5kVI/s1600/1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-n-xrj5dTEtc%2FU8LnkwPfQJI%2FAAAAAAAAI6k%2FhJnAtti5kVI%2Fs1600%2F1.gif&h=ed5d8f5e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"30c7d4bdaa82a7dbf8cf067bd2cc600d6c8ffdad","tid":208043,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T09:29:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6064044a59303cc9316ae408e3b8417392c10849","tid":208043,"uid":83648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T09:30:02.000Z","msg":"桃園一分"},{"pid":"2d470525b783b6a6fe1d0825dc82d5941db7df0b","tid":208043,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T09:51:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>桃園一分</blockquote><br />\n不起訴"},{"pid":"031cb55719a5c8e3e5a8f88db86866b09717756f","tid":208043,"uid":20522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T10:49:21.000Z","msg":"仲以為台灣嘅靜脈注射會有埋中出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}